message.entry: GenPoly length must be greater than one.
GenPoly is not a primitive polynomial. Type warning(''off'',''comm:commsrc:pn:GenPolyNotPrimitive'') to turn off this warning message.
InitialStates vector length must equal the GenPoly order.
CurrentStates vector length must equal the GenPoly order.
Mask vector length must equal the GenPoly order.
Shift must be a scalar value.
GenPoly values must be 0 or 1, or all non-negative integers. Values specified as non-negative integer powers of two must be in strictly decreasing order.
InitialStates and CurrentStates must be equal at object construction.
Only one of the Mask or Shift properties can be specified (but not both).
Input arguments must be parameter-value pairs.
There is no property named ''{0}'' in the commsrc.pn class.
